# FIX_LOGIC.guideline

## CLI VALIDATION
When running in CPU-only mode, strip all VRAM-specific flags (`--highvram`, `--normalvram`, `--lowvram`) and utilize only `--cpu` and `--novram` to prevent Exit Code 2.

## Iteration Rule
If a new error appears:
1. Capture exact traceback from logs.
2. Patch the smallest possible surface (args/deps/paths).
3. Rebuild and re-check runtime/logs.
